note: Livia Blackburne once said: “The process doesn’t end there. Stories are more than just images. As you continue in the tale, you get to know the characters, motivations and conflicts that make up the core of the story.” This phrase caught my attention and inspired me to become a writer, during my studies at Purdue University I realized that writing is not that easy as it seems from the first sight, but I decided to go further and became a prolific writer currently working at mcessay.com
